cedure</strong></h3>\n<p>&#x4ECE;&#x4E0A;&#x9762;&#x7684;&#x622A;&#x56FE;&#x91CC;&#xFF0C;&#x6211;&#x4EEC;&#x8FD8;&#x770B;&#x5230;&#x4E86; The Promise Resolution Procedure &#x7684;&#x8BF4;&#x6CD5;&#x3002;</p>\n<p>&#x5B83;&#x63CF;&#x8FF0;&#x7684;&#x662F;&#xFF0C;&#x4E00;&#x4E9B;&#x7279;&#x6B8A;&#x7684; value &#x88AB; resolve &#x65F6;&#xFF0C;&#x8981;&#x505A;&#x7279;&#x6B8A;&#x5904;&#x7406;&#x3002;&#x8FD9;&#x4E2A;&#x7279;&#x6B8A;&#x5904;&#x7406;&#xFF0C;&#x89C4;&#x8303;&#x4E5F;&#x660E;&#x786E;&#x63CF;&#x8FF0;&#x4E86;&#x3002;</p>\n<p><img alt class=\"lazyload inited\" data-src=\"https://p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/d0ff12f5016d47229bd29f527488aa4a~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-1.image\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"600\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot;?&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;600&quot;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\"></p>\n<p>&#x7B2C;&#x4E00;&#x6B65;&#xFF0C;&#x5982;&#x679C; result &#x662F;&#x5F53;&#x524D; promise &#x672C;&#x8EAB;&#xFF0C;&#x5C31;&#x629B;&#x51FA; TypeError &#x9519;&#x8BEF;&#x3002;</p>\n<p><img alt class=\"lazyload inited\" data-src=\"https://p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/b52e2ec71ec4475c9c90fe66494ab30c~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-1.image\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"600\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot;?&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;600&quot;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\"></p>\n<p>&#x7B2C;&#x4E8C;&#x6B65;&#xFF0C;&#x5982;&#x679C; result &#x662F;&#x53E6;&#x4E00;&#x4E2A; promise&#xFF0C;&#x90A3;&#x4E48;&#x6CBF;&#x7528;&#x5B83;&#x7684; state &#x548C; result &#x72B6;&#x6001;&#x3002;</p>\n<p><img alt class=\"lazyload inited\" data-src=\"https://p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/43316003f80249d8abab0362cb972394~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-1.image\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"600\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;?xml version=&q